# Personal Portfolio — Suhitha

This repository contains a responsive personal portfolio webpage built using **HTML + CSS only**.

## Files
- `index.html` — main HTML
- `style.css` — styles and responsive rules
- `README.md` — this file

## AI Tool Used
I have used creao.ai
## What I did manually (edits & fixes after AI generation)
List the manual changes you made to the AI-generated template (include in your final submission). Example entries (these edits are included in this repo):
- Fixed responsive breakpoints and tuned grid layout for tablet and mobile.
- Replaced placeholder content with real text (name, about statement, skills).
- Implemented CSS-only hamburger using a hidden checkbox for mobile navigation.
- Cleaned and simplified the CSS (box-sizing, container width limits, accessible focus outlines).
- Ensured no horizontal scroll and improved spacing and typography.
- Added semantic HTML structure and anchor navigation for single-page sections.

